<P>You are physician or physiotherapist. You always wanted to subscribe for a  ( Cyriax ) course in Orthopaedic Medicine but did not find
time. This may solve your problem: A hands-on course on Clinical Examination, clinical reasoning and conservative treatment with injections / infiltrations and deep transverse friction of 
soft tissue shoulder lesions is now available on CD. </P>
